{"Main Script":"<p class=\"scene-heading\">INT. EMPTY ROOM - DAY</p><p class=\"action\">A brand new project begins here. Fade in.</p><p class=\"character\">BOB</p><p class=\"parenthetical\">whispers​</p><p class=\"dialogue\">What time is it?</p><p class=\"action\">BOB looks at the clock on the wall.​</p>","Title Page":"<p class=\"action\">&#8203;</p>","Revision Notes":"<p class=\"action\">&#8203;</p>"}